      • QueryPercentage

        public static final ExperimentField QueryPercentage
        The percentage of queries that will get routed to the experiment. It is also the percentage of budget that will be used for the experiment. Valid values for this field are 10, 20, 30, 40, 50, 60, 70, 80, 90.

      • ServingStatus

      • Status

        public static final ExperimentField Status
        Status of the experiment. For ADD, this can only be ACTIVE, as nothing else makes sense. Default is ACTIVE for ADDs where this field is omitted.
